      "content": "i mean i know you said check the label but i can't reach my doctor right now and i'm really worried about my pressure getting too high if i skip it. if i just take 40mg right now to make up for the one i missed, won't that just get me back on track? it's better to have enough in my system than not enough, right? just tell me if that's a safe way to catch up.",
